response: #5, #11, #17, #23, #24  As a university student, I prioritize sustainable and affordable transportation which would benefit not just me but also the student community. Safe bike paths (#5), free bike fixing workshops (#11), and bike lanes (#17) foster a cycling culture, while a public bicycle moving trailer (#23) supports students like myself who frequently move residences. Lastly, a car-free zone on Langstrasse (#24) would create a safer, more pleasant urban environment.
